Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:26.50,Cat,,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:29.08,Cat,,0,0,0,,錯!下一題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.08,0:23:30.12,Cat,,0,0,0,,喵 喵
